        "content": [
            "面对想将满身疮痍的一行人烧尽的焰龙之炎，\\n穆穆凭借爱的力量放出了更猛烈的火焰，\\n并成功击退莱昂尼多。\\n沙音为赎清至今为止的罪孽，\\n加入了王子一行人。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "telop",
            "context": "\\n红莲废道\\n \\n \\n ",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "差不多该解决了吧。\\n嗯？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_1001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "沾满鲜血的胜利之吼。\\n呵呵，看来他们气数已尽了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_1002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "尤蒂尔，\\n有多龙契约在身也难逃一死。\\n已经沉入无穷之河了吧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_1003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120080_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "请、请等一下，阁下！\\n对面向这里走来的那个人影是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我们……绝对不会输！\\n你还好吗，沙音？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "嗯，好不容易被你们救下的性命……\\n我会好好珍惜。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "哼，看来还得由我\\n亲手送你们上路啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "喂，不妙啊！现在的我们\\n哪有余力和这家伙战斗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "退后，尤蒂尔。\\n这里交给我。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "你和埃尔菲莉丝……\\n如果是为了保护两位恩人，我死而无憾。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "莱昂尼多，要打就冲着我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_12"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "我不会让你那么做的。\\n你才应该退下，沙音。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "什么！？闪开，埃尔菲莉丝！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_12"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "让好不容易寻回的家人牺牲，\\n自己苟活于世，这有违伊莉雅的教诲。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_12"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "这里就由身为圣骑士的我来当盾，\\n就算此身被烈火燃尽……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "哼，无聊的闹剧。\\n不管谁当盾，结果都一样。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "你们所有人都会化为灰烬！\\n谁护谁都没用！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "真是的。人类怎么就\\n这么喜欢牺牲自我呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "为了保护别人，让自己去送死。\\n这种事不断重复，都没点长进。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "咦，我说穆穆……\\n你到底站在哪一边啊！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "这不是敌我的问题。我是说，\\n说什么自己死了也没关系的人，\\n只是在赚人眼泪嘛！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "真正的爱，是既保护他人，\\n自己也要活下来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "嚯……难道还有\\n能抵御焰龙之炎的家伙？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "当然有了。\\n只有一位，那就是我。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "少笑死人了，小丫头。刚才是谁\\n在玛斯的火焰下夹着尾巴逃走的啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "嗯，我刚才的确逃走了。\\n但是，多亏了某个人，\\n点燃了我的斗志。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "那个好心到连来杀自己的暗杀者\\n也真心给予救助的女人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_12"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "穆穆……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "看好了，埃尔菲莉丝，\\n什么才是真正的爱。我是不会死的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "我要保护亲爱的，\\n顺便也保护你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "哼，连你那番大话一起烧尽！\\n出来吧，玛斯！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛斯",
            "context": "咕噢噢噢噢噢噢噢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "真是悲哀啊……玛斯。\\n你曾是谁都嫉妒的强大火龙。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "但你却输给了野心，出卖自己的灵魂，\\n成了契约者的傀儡……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "真正的契约才不是那样！\\n靠虚假的爱是成不了最强的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "放马过来吧！\\n你那虚假的火焰，就由我的爱来打败！\\n啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "去死吧，小丫头！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛斯",
            "context": "咕噢噢噢噢噢噢噢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "穆穆！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "哈哈哈哈！都烧成灰烬了吧！\\n玛斯的火焰把一切都……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "嗯！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "呵、呵呵呵呵♪真好笑。\\n你说把一切都……怎么了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "对于现在的我来说，\\n这点程度连蚊子叮都算不上。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "什么！？那个形态是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "多亏你送我这么多炎之魔力，\\n一不小心就进化啦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "成为了能让任何敌人\\n都瞬间灰飞烟灭的超级穆穆！\\n虽然只是暂时的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "不可能！居然吸收了\\n曾毁灭上百个王国的焰龙之炎！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "上百个王国？别开玩笑了！\\n我可是它的3倍……\\n在追逐跨越300年的恋情呢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "现在该轮到我了！\\n让你领教一下\\n恋爱中的火龙有多么火热吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "必杀！300万的热恋之力，\\n终极·火热国度！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "这火焰……\\n唔啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "啊哈哈！什么第一王子！\\n要有点自知之明啊，少爷！\\n哎呀？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "唔……可恶！虽然只是一小步，\\n但竟然让我退后了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "没想到还挺精神的……\\n有两下子嘛。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "哼，既然已经得到了魔神之力，\\n就没必要搞这些小打小闹了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "尤蒂尔，你记住。\\n世界变革之时即将来临。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "执迷旧世力量之人，无法成就霸业。\\n你就和你的龙一起消逝吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "他终于走了。\\n那么……嘿！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "我可不会乖乖奉上\\n亲爱的你的性命。哼哼♪",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "辛苦了。\\n谢谢你保护了我，穆穆。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "哎呀～以我们俩的亲密关系，\\n这点小事应该的嘛♪",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "而且还从废物玛斯那里\\n得到了很多火之魔力。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "回到圣城之后，\\n我们建一座火之龙哭碑\\n作为我们爱的证明吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_12"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "好、好厉害。\\n不仅没被玛斯打倒，反而……\\n穆穆还真是精明啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "好，差不多该回圣城了。\\n沙音，你也一起……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "不，我……不能去。\\n过去我犯下了许多过错。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "为了给予自己惩罚，\\n我要独自一人踏上赎罪之旅。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_1005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_12"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "怎么会……沙音……我还以为\\n能像以前那样一起生活……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "原谅我。像我这种人\\n想追求安逸什么的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_1006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "沙音，你独自踏上旅途，\\n真的能够赎罪吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_1007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "诶？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_1008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "有很多民众前来圣城寻求救援，\\n其中多是些迷途之人和孩子们。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_1009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "如果你真的想赎罪，不是应该\\n为这些人献出自己的力量吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_1010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "可、可是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_1011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你的确曾误入歧途，\\n但是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_1012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你在歧途中收获的东西，\\n并不完全是虚假的，包括你那份力量。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_1013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "有些事，只有历经悲痛的你\\n才能做到，所以……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_1014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "助我一臂之力吧。为了民众，\\n为了未来，也为了我想创造\\n所有人都能欢笑的国家这个梦想。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_1015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "所有人……都能欢笑的国家……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_1016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "原来如此，这宽广的胸怀……\\n我似乎能理解埃尔菲莉丝\\n为什么会追随你了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_1017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "我已污秽不堪的剑和心……\\n如果你连这也愿意接受……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_1018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "我便忍辱负重，为你所用吧，\\n叛变的王子。\\n败军之兵，本就没有什么自由。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_1019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_12"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "沙音！那么……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_1020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "别把我当作伙伴……\\n我已经见过太多人心的黑暗，\\n无法再谈什么情谊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_1021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "我只求用这已死过一次的躯壳，\\n来赎清自己的罪孽……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_1022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "telop",
            "context": "\\n火焰都市巴尔加海姆\\n王座大厅\\n \\n ",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "尤蒂尔吗……\\n王族中居然还有那种家伙。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0072",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "但是天空中闪耀的星只能有一颗。\\n不管是谁，敢跟我作对，\\n都只有陨落一途。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0073",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "比起这些，更让我在意的\\n是另一个家伙的企图……\\n占据了巫女躯体的那个家伙。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0074",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "取回了“一部分”，接下来\\n会如何行动呢，塞西娅？不……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0075",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "魔神莫尔托梅塞亚！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_1023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "telop",
            "context": "\\n狄涅尔帝国　帝都\\n皇帝之殿\\n \\n ",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "皇帝陛下，\\n您玉体如何？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0076",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皇帝塞西娅",
            "context": "嗯，已经逐渐适应巫女的躯体。\\n我的身体也基本都回收了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0077",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皇帝塞西娅",
            "context": "接下来……\\n只剩最大的那“一部分”了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0078",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皇帝塞西娅",
            "context": "不过，暂且静观其变吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0079",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皇帝塞西娅",
            "context": "看看最后一位王族……\\n那位“公主”会采取什么行动。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_08_0080",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
